         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year 39 of Caesar [. . . ] Harthotes son of Marres [. . . acknowledges] receiving from Theon [. . . ? thea]gos of the [ . . .] in Philadelphia [. . .] . . . [. . .] principal of (number missing) drachmas [. . .] . . . [. . .] to Theon . . . [. . .] according to the law [. . .] by Theon [. . .] . . . [. . .] as stated above: [NN wrote for him] upon request because [he says he does not know letters.]
</ab>
